02:19.222 --> 02:21.100
Lois-- the caulking.

02:21.141 --> 02:22.183
Hal...

02:22.225 --> 02:22.893
MALCOLM:

02:22.225 --> 02:22.893
A hot tub.

02:22.935 --> 02:24.185
Sweet.

02:24.227 --> 02:26.229
This is just what

02:24.227 --> 02:26.229
it's like here.

02:26.271 --> 02:28.356
We're always getting

02:26.271 --> 02:28.356
great stuff like hot tubs.

02:28.398 --> 02:29.357
Hal, you're taking it back.

02:29.399 --> 02:30.484
What about the boys?

