Don't they get a say in this?

02:31.902 --> 02:33.612
Yeah, Mom, it'll be great

02:33.654 --> 02:34.863
for entertaining.

02:34.905 --> 02:36.364
No, they do not get

02:34.905 --> 02:36.364
a say in this

02:36.406 --> 02:38.241
because we are

02:36.406 --> 02:38.241
not keeping it.

02:38.283 --> 02:40.285
Well, we're...

02:38.283 --> 02:40.285
kind of locked in.

02:40.327 --> 02:42.496
We're what?

02:40.327 --> 02:42.496
Lois, you

02:40.327 --> 02:42.496
don't get

02:42.537 --> 02:45.206
deals like this

02:42.537 --> 02:45.206
without making a commitment.

